-- Guinea's New President Alpha Conde Pledges Economic, Political Stability
-- B y   O u g n a   C a m a r a
-- 2010-12-21T15:51:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-21/guinea-s-new-president-alpha-conde-pledges-economic-political-stability.html
Alpha Conde was sworn in as
president of Guinea today, promising political and economic
stability in his inaugural speech in the capital, Conakry.  Conde plans to modernize the army and promote good
governance, he told cheering supporters.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
